I am exactly 6 feet tall. I am a simple & private young woman. I love helping people and reaching out to others secretly - hate the limelight or taking any credit for any good I do. I feel the world is in dire need of people who will reach out to others without the crave for been heard or been seen or been applauded.
Lets try to reach out to people without them having to ask or beg, you can do it secretly without anyone ever finding out. I believe its such good deeds that God sees anyway.
